
<item rdf:about='http://www.ietf.org/internet-drafts/draft-ietf-armd-problem-statement-04.txt'>
    <title>"Address Resolution Problems in Large Data Center Networks", Thomas Narten, Manish Karir, Ian Foo</title>
    <link>http://www.ietf.org/internet-drafts/draft-ietf-armd-problem-statement-04.txt</link>
    <description>This document examines address resolution issues related to the scaling of data centers with a very large numbers of hosts.  The initial scope is relatively narrow.  Specifically, it focuses on address resolution (ARP and ND) within the data center.</description>
